						               													<description>In Rise of Man: Stone Age, you are a tribal leader, and you&amp;rsquo;ll have to gather actual resources from the Stone Age period to triumph. You&amp;rsquo;ll fight saber tooth tigers, hunt woolly mammoths, gather food and herbs, build shelters, weather the environment, and overcome any obstacle that the Stone Age will throw at you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rise of Man: Stone Age is a strategic card drafting board game. Players will choose Resources specific to the Stone Age to overcome Obstacles and Hazards that they will face in each of the 5 Rounds of play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As tribal leaders, players must overcome a new Obstacle (or Hazard) in each of the 5 rounds of play by choosing and accumulating suitable Resource cards. At the end of each Round, players earn points for overcoming Obstacles, but lose points by failing to overcome their Obstacles. Resource cards accumulate each round so that players can also play &amp;ldquo;Special Events&amp;rdquo; to earn additional points. Special Events are played by using different combinations of specific Resource Cards. Special Events include Chieftain, Feast, Shaman, and many others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You&amp;rsquo;ll build a life for yourself and your tribe to really create something worth fighting for. Here, it&amp;rsquo;s not victory or defeat, but life or death, and it&amp;rsquo;s all up to the choices that you make.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
